<div class="post">
<div class="inner" id="msg_997278"><div class="quoteheader"><div class="topslice_quote"><a href="?PHPSESSID=608b062285b07a8dd1e4c54d0838ba14&amp;topic=109515.msg997278#msg997278">引述: Eillnvtha 于 2019-05-31, 周五 20:48:26</a></div></div><blockquote class="bbc_standard_quote">&nbsp; &nbsp; 预言之系法术点<br>&nbsp; &nbsp; 在第五纪元之书(Book of the Fifth Age)第五章中描述的基础术法规则规定了以“起效时区”列表决定了施展预言法术的难度和所消耗的法术点「在第五纪元参考卡上给出的IVc列表(chart IVc on the Fifth Age reference card)」。然而该表只列出了窥探今后「或先前」一个月或以内的法术消耗。也许英雄们会想要沿着时光之河看得更远，故事叙述者可以使用下面的拓展表「或是自己规定一个」。<br>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;IVc<br>时区&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 难度<br>1分钟&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;1<br>1小时&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;2<br>1天&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;3<br>1周&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;4<br>1月&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;5<br>1年&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;6<br>10年&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 7<br>100年&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;8<br>1000年&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 9<br>&nbsp; &nbsp; 故事叙述者可能会规定，预知未来比回顾过去更加困难，在这种情况下，他们可能会选择上面的列表作为审视过去的法术的依据，但放眼未来的法术消耗的法术点将会加倍。<br></blockquote><div class="quotefooter"><div class="botslice_quote"></div></div></div>
