<div class="post">
<div class="inner" id="msg_1005349"><div class="quoteheader"><div class="topslice_quote"><a href="?PHPSESSID=608b062285b07a8dd1e4c54d0838ba14&amp;topic=109515.msg1005349#msg1005349">引述: Eillnvtha 于 2019-07-17, 周三 09:51:30</a></div></div><blockquote class="bbc_standard_quote">&nbsp; &nbsp; 『召唤之系法术点<br>第五纪元之书中的基础术法规则提供了决定召唤法术的难度与所消耗法术点的表格，不过，“范围”列表只涉及召唤距离非常有限的法术。如果英雄们想要移动更远的距离「或从更远的地方召唤」，故事讲述者可以使用本拓展表「或者自己规定一个」。<br>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Ⅱ<br>范围&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 难度<br>个人&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;1&nbsp; <br>近战&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;2&nbsp; <br>近距投掷&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;3&nbsp; <br>远距投掷&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;4&nbsp; <br>轰击&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;5&nbsp; <br>视线范围&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;6&nbsp; <br>地区&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;7&nbsp; <br>王国&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;8&nbsp; <br>大陆&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;9&nbsp; <br>异位面&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;可变*&nbsp; <br>*异位面范围应用于元素位面生物的召唤，目前凡人还无法在诸位面之间穿行。不管怎样，创造穿越位面疆界的连接既困难又危险，其困难程度取决于故事讲述者的具体规定，推荐不低于10。其危险之处在于，虽然术士无法把他自己送到别的位面，但如果被召唤的生物同样拥有召唤之系的技能，就可以将术士拖到它的故乡，经历这些后还没有已知的幸存者。』<br></blockquote><div class="quotefooter"><div class="botslice_quote"></div></div></div>
